Interface SBOLDocument

public interface SBOLDocument
extends SBOLVisitable
    The top level container for SBOL objects. This class represents how SBOL objects are grouped in a serialized file.

    • Method Detail

      • getContents

        List<SBOLRootObject> getContents()
        Deprecated. 
        Returns the top-level objects contained in this document. Top level objects may contain other SBOL objects. For example, a DnaComponent may contain a DnaSequence and multiple SequenceAnnotations which will not be included in the results of this function. To get all the objects contained in a document you can use the SBOLObjectCollector function.

      • addContent

        void addContent(SBOLRootObject obj)
        Deprecated. 
        Adds a new top level object to the document. Only top-level objects need to be added explicitly to a document.

      • removeContent

        void removeContent(SBOLRootObject obj)
        Deprecated. 
        Removes a top level object from the document.
